          Gets a list of overlapping annotations public Collection getOverlappers(AnnotationReader other) { Set overlappers = new TreeSet(); Iterator chrIt = other.getChromosomeIterator(); while(chrIt.hasNext()) { String chr = chrIt.next(); Iterator annotationIt = other.getChromosomeTree(chr).valueIterator(); IntervalTree tree = getChromosomeTree(chr); if(tree == null) { continue; } while(annotationIt.hasNext()) { LightweightGenomicAnnotation annot = annotationIt.next(); Iterator overlapperIt = new IntervalTree.ValuesIterator(tree.overlappers(annot.getStart(), annot.getEnd())); while(overlapperIt.hasNext()) { T overlapper = overlapperIt.next(); overlappers.add(overlapper); } } } return overlappers; }
